Lines.Comment: If fighting is what is required, then I shall be ready.
Come... Let us fight for home, for family, and for honor.
Ugh. I grow weary of this.
Ah, it is good to see you friend.
You dare mock me? We will see who laughs last!
I see the gods wish to test my patience today!
Ah, the gods favor me with your presence!
Well, I see that this shall be a productive endeavor.
You? I see fate can make for some unlikely allies.
Baelog: You look way more useful than Olaf and Erik. This is going to be easy!
Olaf: You up for some cake and pie later, buddy?
Fight for the glory of the horde!
Let us march onward to victory!
It is good to fight beside you, friend.
